General.Name: One Software Technologies Ltd
General.Description: One Software Technologies Ltd provides software, hardware, and integration services. The company also offers infrastructure services; organizational solutions; professional managed services; and software solutions for cloud, BI, digital, cyber and security, POS, callup, and other products. It serves governmental, education, industry and trade, technology and hi-tech, financial, municipal, security, and retailing sectors. The company is based in Petah Tikva, Israel.
